text: Erechthias stilbella is a species of moth in the family Tineidae. It was described by Edward Doubleday in 1843. This species is endemic to New Zealand. ==References== ==External links== *Image of type specimen of Erechthias stilbella Category:Moths described in 1843 Category:Erechthiinae Category:Moths of New Zealand Category:Endemic fauna of New Zealand Category:Taxa named by Edward Doubleday
